<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>مَكَّةُ السِّدْرِ<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span>مِنْ بَطْنِ فَخٍّ إِلَى الْمَحْدَثِ.<a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span>⦗١٨٦⦘<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c5">قَالَ الْحَارِثُ بْنُ خَالِدٍ أَوْ غَيْرُهُ فِيهَا:</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[البحر الطويل]</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>إِلَى طَلَلٍ بِالْجَزْعِ مِنْ مَكَّةَ السِّدْرِ ... لِلَيْلَى عَفَا بَيْنَ الْمُشَقَّرِ فَالْحَضَرِ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>فَظَلْتُ وَظَلَّ الْقَوْمُ فِي غَيْرِ حَاجَةٍ ... كَذَا غُدْوَةً حَتَّى دَنَتْ حَزَّةُ الْعَصْرِ<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>